<li>Sign up for new design and Liquid Glass activities in the new year.</li>
<li>Check out the latest additions to our ever-expanding video library.</li>
<li>Meet the team behind the sticker-centric language-learning app <em>CapWords.</em></li>
<li>Browse new documentation and HIG updates.</li>
</ul>
